      "title": "Fuel delivery in Mannar today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The operation of distributing fuel through fuel cards to the villages under Mannar City Divisional Secretariat Division will be carried out again today (17) morning.",
        "I.O.C. located on Thalaimannar main road. Fuel will be supplied at the fuel filling station under the supervision of Divisional Secretariat under the arrangement of District Secretariat."
      ],
